casebody.data:
Breanna BURNS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1513 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. JULY 24, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and EMAS and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of prohibition, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
